│ multifaceted approach that considers your target audience, game genre, budget, and key │
│ performance indicators (KPIs).                                                         │
│                                                                                        │
│ 1.  **Define Your Target Audience:** Clearly identify your ideal player. What are      │
│ their demographics, interests, and gaming habits? This will inform your ad targeting   │
│ and messaging.                                                                         │
│                                                                                        │
