│ notifications and offer exclusive in-game rewards.                                     │
│     *   *Social Media:* Build a community on platforms where your target audience      │
│ spends time. Share development updates, concept art, and behind-the-scenes content.    │
│     *   *Influencer Marketing:* Partner with gaming influencers and content creators   │
│ to showcase your game to their audience.                                               │
│                                                                                        │
